<p>
<note n="0284005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284005">第四＝第二十四【明】＊</note>
<note n="0284006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284006">（論）＋應【宋】【元】，（釋）＋應【明】</note>
<note n="0284007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284007">〔第二之一〕－【宋】【元】【宮】，第二之一＝第二此品有三章【明】</note>
<note n="0284008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284008">相章第一＝章第一【元】，差別章第一【明】</note>
<note n="0284009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284009">阿梨耶識＝阿黎耶識【三】下同</note>
