<note n="0285002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0285002">於＝彌【三】</note>
<note n="0286001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286001">〔差別章第二〕－【明】</note>
<note n="0286002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286002">成立＝立成【明】</note>
<note n="0286003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286003">若＝苦【宮】</note>
<note n="0286004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286004">諸＝論【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0287001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287001">切＝物【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0287002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287002">知＝智【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0287003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287003">得＝行【宮】</note>
<note n="0287004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287004">三之初＝三【宋】【元】【宮】，二之一【明】</note>
<note n="0287005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287005">竟＝究【明】</note>
<note n="0287006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287006">臣＝中【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0287007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287007">似＝以【宮】</note>
<note n="0288001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0288001">抂＝枉【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0289001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0289001">客＝空【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0289002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0289002">惟＝唯【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0289003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0289003">取＝起【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0289004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0289004">〔論曰…別〕七十六字－【明】</note>
